name: Jason Wells
description: My name is Jason Wells, I am 49 years and am a soldier from the U.S.A army but i am now in Iraq for peace keeping and will be coming home within two months time.Am honest,kind caring,affectionate,good sense of humor,easy going,free thinker,trustworthy and respect the lives of other people…..I’m a man who lives life as it comes to me.
